Bettercap
Swiss Army knife for network attacks

Sniffing & Spoofing
Description
Bettercap is a powerful, flexible network attack and monitoring framework. Successor to ettercap with WiFi, Bluetooth, and more.

Installation / Check
Check if installed:

which bettercap
Install command:

sudo apt install bettercap
Basic Syntax
sudo bettercap
